  "text": "Note that the optimization problem (31) is not jointly convex over the variables (P D , P H , M u ). Moreover, it is nonlinear because of the existence of cross terms P H M u and P D M u . In order to remove the nonlinearities and make the two constraints jointly convex, following [CITATION_1] , we reformulate the problem by seeking common solutions of P D and P H , and changing variables to M p := P M u . ",
